The documents provide information that the music and lyrics for "The Drowsy Chaperone" are written by Lisa Lambert and Greg Morrison. Therefore, it's accurate to say that Lisa Lambert performs the role of composing (or co-composing) the music for this musical, even though typically we might refer to her as a composer rather than strictly as a performer in the context of creating the score.
